{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-4">
    Goat Funded Trader offers a variety of evaluation programs, catering to different risk levels. You can choose from One-Step, Two-Step, and Three-Step evaluations, each with its own profit targets and drawdown limits, or Instant Funding accounts, which skip the evaluation phase entirely.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    While the prop firm offers flexibility with no time limits, each challenge and funded account comes with specific rules and conditions that you need to consider carefully.
  </p>

  <!-- Challenge summary cards -->
  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">One-Step Challenge</p>
      <p>Requires a 10% profit target with a 4% daily drawdown and 6% max drawdown. Fastest route to funding but the strictest limits. Account sizes from $15K to $200K ($138–$798).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Two-Step Challenge (Goat & Standard)</p>
      <p>Split evaluation into two stages. Goat variant has lower targets (8%/6%) while Standard requires 10%/5%. Account sizes from $5K to $200K ($22–$730). Best balance of difficulty and cost.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Three-Step Challenge</p>
      <p>Slowest route — three phases each requiring 6% profit target with 8% max drawdown. Account sizes from $10K to $200K ($48–$498). Best for conservative, steady traders.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Instant Funding</p>
      <p>Skip the evaluation entirely. Higher fees and stricter rules (3–4% daily DD, 6–8% max DD). No profit target required. Goat variant from $5K–$100K ($107–$767), Standard from $2.5K–$50K ($73–$1,434).</p>
